    "name": "Behemoth Hippopotamus",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "The behemoth hippopotamus is a true monster. Standing taller than an elephant, this animal has few enemies in the natural world\u2014even dinosaurs and dire crocodiles avoid fights with them. Making them even more dangerous is the fact that they are practically carnivores\u2014while not above eating plant matter, they devour carrion or foolish creatures that come too close."
        }
    ],
